quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,By the fig and the olive
  95,2,and by mount Sinai
  95,3,and by this safe land
  95,4,(that) We have certainly created the human being in the best form
  95,5,then We returned him to the lowest of low
  95,6,"except those who believed and did good works, so there is an unending reward for them"
  95,7,So what makes you deny the way of life (or the judgment day) after this
  95,8,Is not God the wisest of the judges